/font></a>), University of Science and Technology of China</h5><h5 id="Sep-2002-–-Jun-2006-Bachelor-of-Physics-School-of-Physics-and-Electronic-Engineering-Ludong-University-of-China"><a href="#Sep-2002-–-Jun-2006-Bachelor-of-Physics-School-of-Physics-and-Electronic-Engineering-Ludong-University-of-China" class="headerlink" title="Sep, 2002 – Jun, 2006    Bachelor of Physics, School of Physics and Electronic Engineering,  Ludong University of China"></a>Sep, 2002 – Jun, 2006    Bachelor of Physics, School of Physics and Electronic Engineering,  Ludong University of China</h5><h4 id="Employment"><a href="#Employment" class="headerlink" title="Employment:"></a><font color=steelblue>Employment:</font></h4><h5 id="Sep-2017-–-Present-Associate-Professor-Jiangsu-University-of-Science-and-Technology-China"><a href="#Sep-2017-–-Present-Associate-Professor-Jiangsu-University-of-Science-and-Technology-China" class="headerlink" title="Sep, 2017 – Present, Associate Professor, Jiangsu University of Science and Technology, China"></a>Sep, 2017 – Present, Associate Professor, Jiangsu University of Science and Technology, China</h5><h5 id="Oct-2018-–-Oct-2019-Visiting-Scholar-Supervisor-Pro-H-Eugene-Stanley-and-Pro-Shlomo-Havlin-Boston-University-U-S-A"><a href="#Oct-2018-–-Oct-2019-Visiting-Scholar-Supervisor-Pro-H-Eugene-Stanley-and-Pro-Shlomo-Havlin-Boston-University-U-S-A" class="headerlink" title="Oct, 2018 – Oct, 2019 Visiting Scholar (Supervisor: Pro. H. Eugene Stanley and Pro. Shlomo Havlin), Boston University, U.S.A"></a>Oct, 2018 – Oct, 2019 Visiting Scholar (Supervisor: Pro. <a href="http://polymer.bu.edu/hes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><font color=white>H. Eugene Stanley</font></a> and Pro. <a href="http://havlin.biu.ac.il/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><font color=white>Shlomo Havlin</font></a>), Boston University, U.S.A</h5><h5 id="Jan-2012-–-Sep-2017-Lecturer-Jiangsu-University-of-Science-and-Technology-China"><a href="#Jan-2012-–-Sep-2017-Lecturer-Jiangsu-Un